I am very picky about my asian food, being asian myself.
But this place is actually one of best chinese food restaurant in las vegas.
Hubby ad i always go here when we are craving chinese.
The portions are good for the prices they charge.
Since we always do take out, customer service isn't bad.
Of course whenever we do place take out they tell us it'll only be 15 minutes but they are pretty busy so it's usually an additional 10 minutes from what they actually tell you.
I love won ton soup, but im quite picky about it however i will say that hands down this place seems to be the only place that makes really delicious wonton soup.
Great for the wallet and the tummy!

